ss into our accounts. You rolled out Digital Marketing with accounts like 3M and look forward to launching DM into those hard the to reach accounts! Solid contributions and support across all regions in Q2 and look forward to the follow up successes from these campaigns in Q3!\n\n179#Final Regroup on Eps|Pam and Angela- Just a quick note to say thank you both for putting together the last minute regroup this morning on the Episodes campaign. We have all been working in our own little spheres on this one for a while and getting the whole gang together to have a final regroup before officially launching was really helpful. I am glad we were able to hop on a call with short notice, get everyone's questions answered, and finalize next steps quickly and efficiently. Honestly, I think that is how all our meetings should be run.... BADA-BING-BADA-BOOM!   Thanks for putting it together, Angela, and Pam, for being our fearless leader!\n\n180#It Takes an Army|Thank you for putting a ton of time and energy into the ROI Calculator campaign. This campaign literally took an army of people to pull it together. It took research, training, integrations, and many design iterations to make it a successful campaign. I can't thank everyone on the ROI calculator team for going above and beyond to make this campaign happen. Now, it can be used in many different formats, outlets, and move deals along!\n\n181#Constant support and inspiration|Pam- You always make yourself available. Two weeks ago, it was emails at 4am because my daughter broke her arm. Last week it was an after hours call to deliver what could have been unsettling news. This week it was a brainstorming session on what value a conference would bring to Sales and GF. Yesterday it was an impromptu question and answer convo, offering support and guidance. You provide constant support and inspiration no matter the time of day. Thank you so much for all that you do. You really are the true meaning of inspiration!\n\n182#E-VIP Team